00:03:20.090 --> 00:03:22.160 align:middle line:90%
depression and anxiety.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:26.860 align:middle line:84%
So coming from that place of
being always so positive to,

00:03:26.860 --> 00:03:29.580 align:middle line:84%
you know, this happening
