00:03:40.310 --> 00:03:43.460 align:middle line:84%
>> When it happened, I just
spiraled out of control.

00:03:43.460 --> 00:03:46.140 align:middle line:84%
I just had never
dealt with this ever.

00:03:46.140 --> 00:03:48.230 align:middle line:84%
And then I had to
deal with the guilt,

00:03:48.230 --> 00:03:52.220 align:middle line:84%
because my husband, who'd been
an entrepreneur all his life,

00:03:52.220 --> 00:03:54.530 align:middle line:90%
had to start paying the bills.

00:03:54.530 --> 00:03:56.180 align:middle line:84%
So he had to go
and get a job doing

00:03:56.180 --> 00:03:57.980 align:middle line:90%
something he absolutely hated.

00:03:57.980 --> 00:04:00.740 align:middle line:84%
So not only was I having
to deal with the fact

00:04:00.740 --> 00:04:05.640 align:middle line:84%
that we were living on
the breadline, basically.

00:04:05.640 --> 00:04:07.760 align:middle line:84%
He'd come home every
day and look at me,

00:04:07.760 --> 00:04:10.300 align:middle line:84%
and all he wanted to do
was be with his little boy,

00:04:10.300 --> 00:04:11.760 align:middle line:90%
and I put him in this position.

00:04:11.760 --> 00:04:13.730 align:middle line:90%
So the guilt was huge.

00:04:13.730 --> 00:04:15.450 align:middle line:90%
And so for the next four years.

00:04:15.450 --> 00:04:17.660 align:middle line:84%
I just pretty much
became a shell

00:04:17.660 --> 00:04:20.690 align:middle line:84%
