living Groundhog Day.

00:04:20.690 --> 00:04:23.640 align:middle line:84%
I'd just wake up, feed
my child, go to bed,

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:25.030 align:middle line:90%
and that was my life.

00:04:25.030 --> 00:04:27.590 align:middle line:84%
>> And so you experiencing,
at that time, you know,

00:04:27.590 --> 00:04:32.120 align:middle line:84%
difficulty in even leaving
